data.description:
Bring your horses! This haven of beauty and tranquility, nestled on 5.3 acres of mostly fenced land in a country setting, is just minutes from downtown Prattville. This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home with a split floor plan had a new roof put on in 2023 and also comes with a 40x60 barn that includes power and water and a smaller, quaint building for storage.

As you pull up the long, private drive you are met with beautiful views on every side. Both the front and back porches offer plenty of space for entertaining or relaxing. Inside you will find a light and airy vaulted foyer that opens to both the formal living and dining on your right, as well as the great room, also with vaulted ceilings plus a brick fireplace.

Adjacent to the formal and casual living areas is the completely updated kitchen, boasting granite countertops and breakfast room with views of the lush back yard. Just around the corner from the kitchen you will find a hallway with room for a coffee bar, the laundry room, garage entrance, and primary suite with double closets. The primary bathroom includes double sinks, a jetted tub, separate shower and a plethora of storage.

There are three guest bedrooms. Bedroom has its own shower, granting you not one, but two primary bedrooms – both with easy access to the back yard.

Inside the two-story barn with three large overhead doors, you will find everything you need for work or play plus brand new stalls for your horses! In the main area is a vintage cast iron sink, plenty of storage in the back with even more space found in the upstairs loft. There’s more! The barn includes a spacious bunk room with fireplace, its own full bath and four sturdy bunkbeds that fold down from the wall.

Schedule an appointment with your favorite realtor today to tour this beautiful, updated home with must-see amenities. Don’t miss this opportunity to enjoy your very own custom-built home/retreat. It is sure to go fast!
